<br>
This happened because various people &quot;tried to help on CR&quot; and just ended up training Draco to where I was happily recovering from a Rez.  Fortunately the 0.732 seconds it took Draco to roll over me was just enough time for the person who trained me and/or the cleric who rezzed me to Gate.<br>
<br>
I stopped going back in after I realised nobody was listening to me scream in /gu /ooc and /shout &quot;STOP BLOODY WELL ZONING IN AND TRAINING ME PLEASE!&quot;.. (hmm maybe I forgot to use the word please at the time.. but you get the picture).<br>
<br>
The moral to my story.. If you arnt prepared to run around Fear when it is fully popped and find a corpse.. dont do it when Draco is camping my sorry corpse collection.<br>
<br>
Despite my moments of personal misery (which is provided for your amusement).. I had an absolute KICK ASS time in Fear and wanted to say thanks to everyone for comming along.. I am so glad to have finally handed Terror his ass!  <br>
<br>
I loved watching Ace pull 10+ Amys and instead of thinking about how it would hurt thinking how much fun it was going to be taking them down.<br>
